divs: Sighting DetailsI was bringing my daughter in the house when over head I saw what I thought was a bird but then realized this was higher up and left a contrail. it took me about 2 minutes to get the camera but the contrail was a tight spiral with rings by the time the camera turned on the trail had started to fade here are the photos.
Summary: Saw something fly very fast over my head object left a trail.
